snippet.title: The Positive Platform Podcast Episode 37 with Amber Ybarra and The Mental Marketer
snippet.description:
Selling Digital Products online is in a Golden Era. In this video the Mental Marketer discusses how and why he started selling Digital Products online successfully. You can sign up for the Digital Products Secrets Course here: https://www.thementalmarketer.com/digitalproductsecrets

This is the audio portion of the interview with Amber Ybarra and The Mental Marketer. 
.
Episode 37 of The Positive Platform Podcast:
.
Download the episode here: here: https://bit.ly/2Lhl9at
.
In this audio The Mental Marketer discusses his entrepreneurial journey and How You Can Start An Online Business Selling Digital Products.
.
You might say...
. 
Well, what's a Digital Product ❓❓ 🤔
.
Great question...
.
A Digital Product is an intangible asset or piece of media that can be sold and distributed repeatedly online without the need to replenish inventory..
.
So, literally, you create it ONCE and you can sell it an INFINITE amount of times...
.
Without ever having to order more when the supply runs low, or carry any inventory...
.
(Way better than selling t-shirts for $15 bucks a piece and only making $5 after all expenses 🤷)
.
What makes Digital Products really cool is the fact that they can be a business all by themselves, or they can be used to increase the value of an existing product or business.
.
And...
.
The Global market size for Digital Products was 336.14 Billion in 2020 and is expected to reach 400.34 Billion by the end of this year.
.
(Billion, with a B ‼... it's not a typo)
.
So, yeah...
.
Selling Digital products online is a really HOT topic right now.
.
And our conversation brought the heat 🔥
.
